    "summary": "A metal dust explosion and fire occurred at AL Solutions facility while processing zirconium in a blender. The explosion initiated when zirconium particulates ignited due to metal-to-metal contact between blender blades and sidewall. Three employees died and one contractor was injured. The explosion and fire damaged the production building and caused plant shutdown.",
